<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77aacd4d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s459b–8"><num value="459b–8">§ 459b–8.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of sections 459b to 459b–8 of this title; except that no more than $42,917,575 shall be appropriated for the acquisition of land and waters and improvements thereon, and interests therein, and incidental costs relating thereto, in accordance with the provisions of such sections.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77aacd4e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/126/s9">Pub. L. 87–126, § 9</ref>, <date date="1961-08-07">Aug. 7, 1961</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/75/293">75 Stat. 293</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/91/252">Pub. L. 91–252</ref>, <date date="1970-05-14">May 14, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/216">84 Stat. 216</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/98/141/s3">Pub. L. 98–141, § 3</ref>, <date date="1983-10-31">Oct. 31, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/909">97 Stat. 909</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
